title: 140th Sitting of the Committee on Constitutional and Legislative Issues (Narodna Skupstina Republike Srbije)
text: ( Source : Narodna Skupstina Republike Srbije) The MPs had submitted 61 amendments to the Bill amending and modifying the Railway Law. The Committee members found two of the amendments non-compliant with the Constitution and the legal system
